DialogueNode.dialogue: Hi Janet! How are you doing today?
Not too bad. I went to the gym after work yesterday for the first time in a while so I'm a bit sore today.
Pretty well. I'm not a huge fan of this weather. Snow in April is ridiculous!
Oh really? I go to the gym every day after work. Funny I didn't see you there.
Right? It feels like it's been winter for like 5 months.
Oh, hi Alex. I'm doing well what about you?
Oh.... ha, haha. I must've missed you somehow. Now that I think about it I've gotta get some work done.
I don't know if Spring will ever come. I will never get used to this.
Mhm. I'll see you around, Alex.
Me neither. Well, I'd better get back to work. It was good talking to you Alex.
